    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b Looking for a ride that\u2019s practically brand new? You\u2019ve found it! This car is in absolute pristine condition\u2014spotless inside and out, and it drives like a total dream. I\u2019ve babied this beauty since day one, and it shows. It\u2019s seriously like it just rolled off the lot! If you want a top-tier vehicle that\u2019s been loved and cared for, this is the one for you. Drop me a message and let\u2019s get you behind the wheel! \u2728",
