      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty. It is in absolutely stunning shape\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, so the interior is spotless and the paint is glowing. It drives like an absolute dream and has been kept in a climate-controlled garage. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership headache, this is the one for you. Drop me a message, I'd love to show it to you!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
